        <mxCell id="4mRV1LXF5f9laapuvszc-288" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Trained Autoencoder&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Reasoning: Find top hpo word contributions with binary vector of patient and disease &amp;amp; weights through decoder&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;patient_vector&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼb&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;disease_vectors&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;top_disease_idx&lt;/span&gt;][&lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼb&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;weight&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;reconstructed&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span class=&quot;ͼb&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;][&lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;]  &lt;span class=&quot;ͼ6&quot;&gt;# optional, importance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;contributing_terms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ͼ8&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;append((&lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;hpo&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;ͼe&quot;&gt;weight&lt;/span&gt;))&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;For TF-IDF, it&#39;s the same but only instead of HPO terms use words&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
